#. <section class="sutta" id="mn4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn4:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 4"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn4:0.2"
msgid "Bhayabheravasutta"
msgstr "Fear and Terror"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn4:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Jāṇussoṇi went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

#. VAR: sāraṇīyaṃ → sārāṇīyaṃ (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "mn4:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

# Bodhi, Nyanamoli, and Thanissaro translate this as a question. However, there are none of the usual question markers and given the varied sequence as evident in the EA version (see Analayo) it seems likely that Horner was right to translate as a statement.
#. VAR: samādapetā → samādāpetā (?)
msgctxt "mn4:2.3"
msgid ""
"“yeme, bho gotama, kulaputtā bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ uddissa saddhā agārasmā "
"anagāriyaṃ pabbajitā, bhavaṃ tesaṃ gotamo pubbaṅgamo, bhavaṃ tesaṃ gotamo "
"bahukāro, bhavaṃ tesaṃ gotamo samādapetā;"
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, those members of good families who have gone forth from the "
"lay life to homelessness out of faith in Master Gotama have Master Gotama to "
"lead the way, help them out, and give them encouragement."

msgctxt "mn4:2.4"
msgid "bhoto ca pana gotamassa sā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjatī”ti."
msgstr "And those people follow Master Gotama’s example.”"

msgctxt "mn4:2.5"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa."
msgstr "“That’s so true, brahmin! That’s so true, brahmin! …”"

msgctxt "mn4:2.6"
msgid ""
"Ye te, brāhmaṇa, kulaputtā mamaṃ uddissa saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajitā, ahaṃ tesaṃ pubbaṅgamo, ahaṃ tesaṃ bahukāro, ahaṃ tesaṃ samādapetā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:2.7"
msgid "mama ca pana sā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""

# Note that BB renders this phrase differently here and at AN 10.99
msgctxt "mn4:2.8"
msgid ""
"“Durabhisambhavāni hi kho, bho gotama, araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni, dukkaraṃ pavivekaṃ, durabhiramaṃ "
msgstr ""
"“But Master Gotama, remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest are "
"challenging. It’s hard to maintain seclusion and hard to find joy in it. "

msgctxt "mn4:2.9"
msgid "ekatte, haranti maññe mano vanāni samādhiṃ alabhamānassa bhikkhuno”ti."
msgstr ""
"Staying alone, the forests seem to rob the mind of a mendicant who isn’t "
"immersed in samādhi.”"

msgctxt "mn4:2.10"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa."
msgstr "“That’s so true, brahmin! That’s so true, brahmin! …"

msgctxt "mn4:2.11"
msgid ""
"Durabhisambhavāni hi kho, brāhmaṇa, araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni, "
"dukkaraṃ pavivekaṃ, durabhiramaṃ ekatte, haranti maññe mano vanāni samādhiṃ "
"alabhamānassa bhikkhuno."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:3.1"
msgid ""
"Mayhampi kho, brāhmaṇa, pubbeva sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva "
"sato etadahosi:"
msgstr ""
"Before my awakening—when I was still unawakened but intent on awakening—I "
"too thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘durabhisambhavāni hi kho araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni, dukkaraṃ "
"pavivekaṃ, durabhiramaṃ "
msgstr ""
"‘Remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest are challenging. It’s hard "
"to maintain seclusion, and hard to find joy in it. "

msgctxt "mn4:3.3"
msgid "ekatte, haranti maññe mano vanāni samādhiṃ alabhamānassa bhikkhuno’ti."
msgstr ""
"Staying alone, the forests seem to rob the mind of a mendicant who isn’t "
"immersed in samādhi.’"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:4.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā aparisuddhakāyakammantā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"aparisuddhakāyakammantasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins with unpurified conduct of body, speech, "
"and mind who frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "
"Those ascetics and brahmins summon unskillful fear and terror because of "
"these defects in their conduct."

msgctxt "mn4:4.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ aparisuddhakāyakammanto araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""
"But I don’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest with "
"unpurified conduct of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "mn4:4.4"
msgid "parisuddhakāyakammantohamasmi."
msgstr "My conduct is purified."

msgctxt "mn4:4.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā parisuddhakāyakammantā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""
"I am one of those noble ones who frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness "
"and the forest with purified conduct of body, speech, and mind.’"

msgctxt "mn4:4.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, parisuddhakāyakammataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (1)"
msgstr ""
"Seeing this purity of conduct in myself I felt even more unruffled about "
"staying in the forest. "

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5-7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:5-7.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.2"
msgid "‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā aparisuddhavacīkammantā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.3"
msgid "aparisuddhamanokammantā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.4"
msgid ""
"aparisuddhājīvā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"aparisuddhājīvasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins with unpurified livelihood who frequent "
"remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. Those ascetics and "
"brahmins summon unskillful fear and terror because of these defects in their "
"livelihood."

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.5"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ aparisuddhājīvo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""
"But I don’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest with "
"unpurified livelihood."

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.6"
msgid "parisuddhājīvohamasmi."
msgstr "My livelihood is purified."

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.7"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā parisuddhājīvā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""
"I am one of those noble ones who frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness "
"and the forest with purified livelihood.’"

msgctxt "mn4:5-7.8"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, parisuddhājīvataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (2–4.)"
msgstr ""
"Seeing this purity of livelihood in myself I felt even more unruffled about "
"staying in the forest."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:8.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā abhijjhālū kāmesu tibbasārāgā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"abhijjhālukāmesutibbasārāgasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā "
"akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins full of desire for sensual pleasures, with "
"acute lust …"

msgctxt "mn4:8.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ abhijjhālu kāmesu tibbasārāgo araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:8.4"
msgid "anabhijjhālūhamasmi."
msgstr "I am not full of desire …’"

msgctxt "mn4:8.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā anabhijjhālū araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti, tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:8.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, anabhijjhālutaṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (5)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:9.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā byāpannacittā paduṭṭhamanasaṅkappā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"byāpannacittapaduṭṭhamanasaṅkappasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā "
"akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins full of ill will, with hateful intentions …"

msgctxt "mn4:9.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ byāpannacitto paduṭṭhamanasaṅkappo araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:9.4"
msgid "mettacittohamasmi."
msgstr "I have a heart full of love …’"

msgctxt "mn4:9.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā mettacittā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti "
"tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:9.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, mettacittataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo pallomamāpādiṃ "
"araññe vihārāya. (6)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:10.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā thinamiddhapariyuṭṭhitā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"thinamiddhapariyuṭṭhānasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins overcome with dullness and drowsiness …"

msgctxt "mn4:10.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ thinamiddhapariyuṭṭhito araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:10.4"
msgid "vigatathinamiddhohamasmi."
msgstr "I am free of dullness and drowsiness …’"

msgctxt "mn4:10.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā vigatathinamiddhā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:10.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vigatathinamiddhataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (7)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:11.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā uddhatā avūpasantacittā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"uddhataavūpasantacittasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are restless, with no peace of mind …"

msgctxt "mn4:11.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ uddhato avūpasantacitto araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:11.4"
msgid "vūpasantacittohamasmi."
msgstr "My mind is peaceful …’"

msgctxt "mn4:11.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā vūpasantacittā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti, tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:11.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vūpasantacittataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (8)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:12.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā kaṅkhī vicikicchī araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, kaṅkhivicikicchisandosahetu have te bhonto "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr "‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are doubting and uncertain …"

msgctxt "mn4:12.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ kaṅkhī vicikicchī araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:12.4"
msgid "tiṇṇavicikicchohamasmi."
msgstr "I’ve gone beyond doubt …’"

msgctxt "mn4:12.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā tiṇṇavicikicchā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:12.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, tiṇṇavicikicchataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (9)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:13.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:13.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā attukkaṃsakā paravambhī "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"attukkaṃsanaparavambhanasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who glorify themselves and put others down …"

msgctxt "mn4:13.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ attukkaṃsako paravambhī araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:13.4"
msgid "anattukkaṃsako aparavambhīhamasmi."
msgstr "I don’t glorify myself and put others down …’"

msgctxt "mn4:13.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā anattukkaṃsakā aparavambhī araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:13.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, anattukkaṃsakataṃ aparavambhitaṃ attani sampassamāno "
"bhiyyo pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (10)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:14.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā chambhī bhīrukajātikā araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, chambhibhīrukajātikasandosahetu have te "
"bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr "‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are cowardly and craven …"

msgctxt "mn4:14.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ chambhī bhīrukajātiko araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:14.4"
msgid "vigatalomahaṃsohamasmi."
msgstr "I don’t get startled …’"

msgctxt "mn4:14.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā vigatalomahaṃsā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:14.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vigatalomahaṃsataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (11)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:15.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:15.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā lābhasakkārasilokaṃ nikāmayamānā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"lābhasakkārasilokanikāmanasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who enjoy possessions, honor, and "
"popularity …"

msgctxt "mn4:15.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ lābhasakkārasilokaṃ nikāmayamāno araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:15.4"
msgid "appicchohamasmi."
msgstr "I have few wishes …’"

msgctxt "mn4:15.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā appicchā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti "
"tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:15.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, appicchataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo pallomamāpādiṃ "
"araññe vihārāya. (12)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:16.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:16.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā kusītā hīnavīriyā araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, kusītahīnavīriyasandosahetu have te bhonto "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr "‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are lazy and lack energy …"

msgctxt "mn4:16.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ kusīto hīnavīriyo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:16.4"
msgid "āraddhavīriyohamasmi."
msgstr "I am energetic …’"

msgctxt "mn4:16.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā āraddhavīriyā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:16.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, āraddhavīriyataṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (13)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:17.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:17.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā muṭṭhassatī asampajānā araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, muṭṭhassatiasampajānasandosahetu have te "
"bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are unmindful and lack situational "
"awareness …"

msgctxt "mn4:17.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ muṭṭhassati asampajāno araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:17.4"
msgid "upaṭṭhitassatihamasmi."
msgstr "I am mindful …’"

msgctxt "mn4:17.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā upaṭṭhitassatī araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:17.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, upaṭṭhitassatitaṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (14)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:18.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:18.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā asamāhitā vibbhantacittā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, "
"asamāhitavibbhantacittasandosahetu have te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who lack immersion, with straying minds …"

msgctxt "mn4:18.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ asamāhito vibbhantacitto araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:18.4"
msgid "samādhisampannohamasmi."
msgstr "I am accomplished in immersion …’"

msgctxt "mn4:18.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā samādhisampannā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:18.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, samādhisampadaṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo "
"pallomamāpādiṃ araññe vihārāya. (15)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:19.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:19.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye kho keci samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā duppaññā eḷamūgā araññavanapatthāni "
"pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevanti, duppaññaeḷamūgasandosahetu have te bhonto "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇā akusalaṃ bhayabheravaṃ avhāyanti."
msgstr ""
"‘There are ascetics and brahmins who are witless and stupid who frequent "
"remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. Those ascetics and "
"brahmins summon unskillful fear and terror because of the defects of "
"witlessness and stupidity."

msgctxt "mn4:19.3"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ duppañño eḷamūgo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevāmi;"
msgstr ""
"But I don’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest "
"witless and stupid."

msgctxt "mn4:19.4"
msgid "paññāsampannohamasmi."
msgstr "I am accomplished in wisdom."

msgctxt "mn4:19.5"
msgid ""
"Ye hi vo ariyā paññāsampannā araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni "
"paṭisevanti tesamahaṃ aññataro’ti."
msgstr ""
"I am one of those noble ones who frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness "
"and the forest accomplished in wisdom.’"

msgctxt "mn4:19.6"
msgid ""
"Etamahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, paññāsampadaṃ attani sampassamāno bhiyyo pallomamāpādiṃ "
"araññe vihārāya. (16)"
msgstr ""
"Seeing this accomplishment of wisdom in myself I felt even more unruffled "
"about staying in the forest."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn4:19.7"
msgid "Soḷasapariyāyaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:20.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:20.2"
msgid "‘yannūnāhaṃ yā tā rattiyo abhiññātā abhilakkhitā—"
msgstr "‘There are certain nights that are recognized as specially portentous:"

msgctxt "mn4:20.3"
msgid "cātuddasī pañcadasī aṭṭhamī ca pakkhassa—"
msgstr "the fourteenth, fifteenth, and eighth of the fortnight."

msgctxt "mn4:20.4"
msgid ""
"tathārūpāsu rattīsu yāni tāni ārāmacetiyāni vanacetiyāni rukkhacetiyāni "
"bhiṃsanakāni salomahaṃsāni tathārūpesu senāsanesu vihareyyaṃ appeva nāmāhaṃ "
"bhayabheravaṃ passeyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"On such nights, why don’t I stay in awe-inspiring and hair-raising shrines "
"in parks, forests, and trees? In such lodgings, hopefully I might see that "
"fear and terror.’"

msgctxt "mn4:20.5"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, aparena samayena yā tā rattiyo abhiññātā abhilakkhitā—"
msgstr "Some time later, that’s what I did."

msgctxt "mn4:20.6"
msgid "cātuddasī pañcadasī aṭṭhamī ca pakkhassa—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn4:20.7"
msgid ""
"tathārūpāsu rattīsu yāni tāni ārāmacetiyāni vanacetiyāni rukkhacetiyāni "
"bhiṃsanakāni salomahaṃsāni tathārūpesu senāsanesu viharāmi."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: paṇṇakasaṭaṃ → paṇṇasaṭaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "mn4:20.8"
msgid ""
"Tattha ca me, brāhmaṇa, viharato mago vā āgacchati, moro vā kaṭṭhaṃ pāteti, "
"vāto vā paṇṇakasaṭaṃ ereti;"
msgstr ""
"As I was staying there a deer came by, or a peacock snapped a twig, or the "
"wind rustled the leaves."

#. VAR: tassa mayhaṃ brāhmaṇa etadahosi → tassa mayhaṃ evaṃ hoti (bj, pts1) | tassa mayhaṃ brāhmaṇa evaṃ hoti (s1-3)
msgctxt "mn4:20.9"
msgid "tassa mayhaṃ brāhmaṇa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:20.10"
msgid "‘etaṃ nūna taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchatī’ti."
msgstr "‘Is this that fear and terror coming?’"

msgctxt "mn4:20.11"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then I thought:"

msgctxt "mn4:20.12"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho ahaṃ aññadatthu bhayapaṭikaṅkhī viharāmi?"
msgstr "‘Why do I always meditate expecting that fear and terror to come?"

#. VAR: tathābhūtaṃ tathābhūtova → tathābhūta­tathā­bhūto va (bj) | tathābhūto tathābhūtova (s1-3)
#. VAR: yathābhūtaṃ yathābhūtassa → yathā­bhūta­yathā­bhūtassa (bj) | yathābhūtassa yathābhūtassa (s1-3)
msgctxt "mn4:20.13"
msgid ""
"Yannūnāhaṃ yathābhūtaṃ yathābhūtassa me taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati, "
"tathābhūtaṃ tathābhūtova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivineyyan’ti."
msgstr ""
"Why don’t I get rid of that fear and terror just as it comes, while "
"remaining just as I am?’"

msgctxt "mn4:20.14"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, caṅkamantassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr "Then that fear and terror came upon me as I was walking."

msgctxt "mn4:20.15"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva tiṭṭhāmi na nisīdāmi na nipajjāmi, yāva "
"caṅkamantova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi."
msgstr ""
"I didn’t stand still or sit down or lie down until I had got rid of that "
"fear and terror while walking."

msgctxt "mn4:20.16"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, ṭhitassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr "Then that fear and terror came upon me as I was standing."

msgctxt "mn4:20.17"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva caṅkamāmi na nisīdāmi na nipajjāmi. Yāva "
"ṭhitova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi."
msgstr ""
"I didn’t walk or sit down or lie down until I had got rid of that fear and "
"terror while standing."

msgctxt "mn4:20.18"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, nisinnassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr "Then that fear and terror came upon me as I was sitting."

msgctxt "mn4:20.19"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva nipajjāmi na tiṭṭhāmi na caṅkamāmi, yāva "
"nisinnova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi."
msgstr ""
"I didn’t lie down or stand still or walk until I had got rid of that fear "
"and terror while sitting."

msgctxt "mn4:20.20"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, nipannassa taṃ bhayabheravaṃ āgacchati."
msgstr "Then that fear and terror came upon me as I was lying down."

msgctxt "mn4:20.21"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, neva tāva nisīdāmi na tiṭṭhāmi na caṅkamāmi, yāva "
"nipannova taṃ bhayabheravaṃ paṭivinemi."
msgstr ""
"I didn’t sit up or stand still or walk until I had got rid of that fear and "
"terror while lying down."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:21.1"
msgid ""
"Santi kho pana, brāhmaṇa, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā rattiṃyeva samānaṃ divāti "
"sañjānanti, divāyeva samānaṃ rattīti sañjānanti."
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who perceive that it’s day when in fact "
"it’s night, or perceive that it’s night when in fact it’s day."

msgctxt "mn4:21.2"
msgid "Idamahaṃ tesaṃ samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ sammohavihārasmiṃ vadāmi."
msgstr "This meditation of theirs is delusional, I say."

msgctxt "mn4:21.3"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ kho pana, brāhmaṇa, rattiṃyeva samānaṃ rattīti sañjānāmi, divāyeva "
"samānaṃ divāti sañjānāmi."
msgstr ""
"I perceive that it’s night when in fact it is night, and perceive that it’s "
"day when in fact it is day."

msgctxt "mn4:21.4"
msgid "Yaṃ kho taṃ, brāhmaṇa, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr "And if there’s anyone of whom it may be rightly said that"

msgctxt "mn4:21.5"
msgid ""
"‘asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya "
"lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’ti, mameva taṃ sammā "
"vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr ""
"a being not liable to delusion has arisen in the world for the welfare and "
"happiness of the people, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods and "
"humans, it’s of me that this should be said."

msgctxt "mn4:21.6"
msgid ""
"‘asammohadhammo satto loke uppanno bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya "
"lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22-26"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
#. VAR: asammuṭṭhā → appamuṭṭhā (s1) | appammuṭṭhā (s2, s3)
msgctxt "mn4:22-26.1"
msgid ""
"Āraddhaṃ kho pana me, brāhmaṇa, vīriyaṃ ahosi asallīnaṃ, upaṭṭhitā sati "
"asammuṭṭhā, passaddho kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ cittaṃ ekaggaṃ."
msgstr ""
"My energy was roused up and unflagging, my mindfulness was established and "
"lucid, my body was tranquil and undisturbed, and my mind was immersed in "
"samādhi."

msgctxt "mn4:22-26.2"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi "
"savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"Quite secluded from sensual pleasures, secluded from unskillful qualities, I "
"entered and remained in the first absorption, which has the rapture and "
"bliss born of seclusion, while placing the mind and keeping it connected."

msgctxt "mn4:22-26.3"
msgid ""
"Vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ "
"avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"As the placing of the mind and keeping it connected were stilled, I entered "
"and remained in the second absorption, which has the rapture and bliss born "
"of immersion, with internal clarity and confidence, and unified mind, "
"without placing the mind and keeping it connected."

msgctxt "mn4:22-26.4"
msgid ""
"Pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca vihāsiṃ, sato ca sampajāno sukhañca kāyena "
"paṭisaṃvedesiṃ; yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti: ‘upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ti "
"tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"And with the fading away of rapture, I entered and remained in the third "
"absorption, where I meditated with equanimity, mindful and aware, personally "
"experiencing the bliss of which the noble ones declare, ‘Equanimous and "
"mindful, one meditates in bliss.’"

msgctxt "mn4:22-26.5"
msgid ""
"Sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ "
"atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"With the giving up of pleasure and pain, and the ending of former happiness "
"and sadness, I entered and remained in the fourth absorption, without "
"pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:27.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhininnāmesiṃ. So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarāmi,"
msgstr ""
"When my mind had become immersed in samādhi like this—purified, bright, "
"flawless, rid of imperfections, pliable, workable, steady, and imperturbable—"
"I extended it toward recollection of past lives. I recollected many kinds of "
"past lives."

msgctxt "mn4:27.2"
msgid ""
"seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo "
"pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattālīsampi "
"jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi "
"anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe: ‘"
"amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī "
"evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ; tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo "
"evaṅgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, "
"so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ti. Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ "
"anussarāmi."
msgstr ""
"That is: one, two, three, four, five, ten, twenty, thirty, forty, fifty, a "
"hundred, a thousand, a hundred thousand rebirths; many eons of the world "
"contracting, many eons of the world evolving, many eons of the world "
"contracting and evolving. I remembered: ‘There, I was named this, my clan "
"was that, I looked like this, and that was my food. This was how I felt "
"pleasure and pain, and that was how my life ended. When I passed away from "
"that place I was reborn somewhere else. There, too, I was named this, my "
"clan was that, I looked like this, and that was my food. This was how I felt "
"pleasure and pain, and that was how my life ended. When I passed away from "
"that place I was reborn here.’ And so I recollected my many kinds of past "
"lives, with features and details."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya28"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:28.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, brāhmaṇa, rattiyā paṭhame yāme paṭhamā vijjā adhigatā, "
msgstr ""
"This was the first knowledge, which I achieved in the first watch of the "
"night. "

msgctxt "mn4:28.2"
msgid ""
"avijjā vihatā vijjā uppannā, tamo vihato āloko uppanno, yathā taṃ "
"appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato."
msgstr ""
"Ignorance was destroyed and knowledge arose; darkness was destroyed and "
"light arose, as happens for a meditator who is diligent, keen, and resolute."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya29"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.23"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:29.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte sattānaṃ cutūpapātañāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhininnāmesiṃ."
msgstr ""
"When my mind had become immersed in samādhi like this—purified, bright, "
"flawless, rid of imperfections, pliable, workable, steady, and imperturbable—"
"I extended it toward knowledge of the death and rebirth of sentient beings."

msgctxt "mn4:29.2"
msgid ""
"So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passāmi cavamāne "
"upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage "
"satte pajānāmi: ‘ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā "
"vacīduccaritena samannāgatā manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā "
"micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā; te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā "
"apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā. Ime vā pana bhonto sattā "
"kāyasucaritena samannāgatā vacīsucaritena samannāgatā manosucaritena "
"samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā; te "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ti. Iti dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passāmi cavamāne upapajjamāne "
"hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāmi."
msgstr ""
"With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, I saw sentient beings "
"passing away and being reborn—inferior and superior, beautiful and ugly, in "
"a good place or a bad place. I understood how sentient beings are reborn "
"according to their deeds: ‘These dear beings did bad things by way of body, "
"speech, and mind. They spoke ill of the noble ones; they had wrong view; and "
"they chose to act out of that wrong view. When their body breaks up, after "
"death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "
"These dear beings, however, did good things by way of body, speech, and "
"mind. They never spoke ill of the noble ones; they had right view; and they "
"chose to act out of that right view. When their body breaks up, after death, "
"they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.’ And so, with clairvoyance "
"that is purified and superhuman, I saw sentient beings passing away and "
"being reborn—inferior and superior, beautiful and ugly, in a good place or a "
"bad place. I understood how sentient beings are reborn according to their "
"deeds."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya30"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:30.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, brāhmaṇa, rattiyā majjhime yāme dutiyā vijjā adhigatā, "
msgstr ""
"This was the second knowledge, which I achieved in the middle watch of the "
"night. "

msgctxt "mn4:30.2"
msgid ""
"avijjā vihatā vijjā uppannā, tamo vihato āloko uppanno, yathā taṃ "
"appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato."
msgstr ""
"Ignorance was destroyed and knowledge arose; darkness was destroyed and "
"light arose, as happens for a meditator who is diligent, keen, and resolute."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya31"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:31.1"
msgid ""
"So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese "
"mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte āsavānaṃ khayañāṇāya cittaṃ "
"abhininnāmesiṃ."
msgstr ""
"When my mind had become immersed in samādhi like this—purified, bright, "
"flawless, rid of imperfections, pliable, workable, steady, and imperturbable—"
"I extended it toward knowledge of the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "mn4:31.2"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti "
"yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘"
"ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"I truly understood: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ …"
" ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to "
"the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "mn4:31.3"
msgid ""
"‘Ime āsavā’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’ti yathābhūtaṃ "
"abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘ayaṃ āsavanirodho’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, ‘ayaṃ "
"āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"I truly understood: ‘These are defilements’ … ‘This is the origin of "
"defilements’ … ‘This is the cessation of defilements’ … ‘This is the "
"practice that leads to the cessation of defilements’."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya32"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:32.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa me evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha, bhavāsavāpi "
"cittaṃ vimuccittha, avijjāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccittha."
msgstr ""
"Knowing and seeing like this, my mind was freed from the defilements of "
"sensuality, desire to be reborn, and ignorance."

msgctxt "mn4:32.2"
msgid "Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ ahosi."
msgstr "When it was freed, I knew it was freed."

msgctxt "mn4:32.3"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"abbhaññāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"I understood: ‘Rebirth is ended; the spiritual journey has been completed; "
"what had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of "
"existence.’"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya33"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:33.1"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, brāhmaṇa, rattiyā pacchime yāme tatiyā vijjā adhigatā, "
msgstr ""
"This was the third knowledge, which I achieved in the final watch of the "
"night. "

msgctxt "mn4:33.2"
msgid ""
"avijjā vihatā vijjā uppannā, tamo vihato āloko uppanno, yathā taṃ "
"appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato."
msgstr ""
"Ignorance was destroyed and knowledge arose; darkness was destroyed and "
"light arose, as happens for a meditator who is diligent, keen, and resolute."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya34"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:34.1"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, brāhmaṇa, evamassa:"
msgstr "Brahmin, you might think:"

msgctxt "mn4:34.2"
msgid ""
"‘ajjāpi nūna samaṇo gotamo avītarāgo avītadoso avītamoho, tasmā "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Perhaps the Master Gotama is not free of greed, hate, and delusion even "
"today, and that is why he still frequents remote lodgings in the wilderness "
"and the forest.’"

msgctxt "mn4:34.3"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "But you should not see it like this."

msgctxt "mn4:34.4"
msgid ""
"Dve kho ahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, atthavase sampassamāno araññavanapatthāni pantāni "
"senāsanāni paṭisevāmi—"
msgstr ""
"I see two reasons to frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the "
"forest."

msgctxt "mn4:34.5"
msgid ""
"attano ca diṭṭhadhammasukhavihāraṃ sampassamāno, pacchimañca janataṃ "
"anukampamāno”ti."
msgstr ""
"I see a happy life for myself in the present, and I have compassion for "
"future generations.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya35"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.24"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn4:35.1"
msgid ""
"“Anukampitarūpā vatāyaṃ bhotā gotamena pacchimā janatā, yathā taṃ arahatā "
"sammāsambuddhena."
msgstr ""
"“Indeed, Master Gotama has compassion for future generations, since he is a "
"perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha."

msgctxt "mn4:35.2"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama. Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent, Master Gotama!"

msgctxt "mn4:35.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""
"As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good "
"eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many "
"ways."

msgctxt "mn4:35.4"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant "
"Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn4:35.5"
msgid ""
"Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn4:35.6"
msgid "Bhayabheravasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
